      "text": "Ultranationalist advisers of President Kubitschek have drawn up an anti-US \"disaster plan,\" which they say will go into effect if Washington and the International Monetary Fund (IMF) continue to insist on a \"complete\" exchange reform as a condition of emergency balance-of-payments aid.",
      "char_len": 286,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        8,
        74,
        530,
        86
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 4,
      "serial_label": "L4",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        8,
        92,
        530,
        105
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 5,
      "serial_label": "L5",
      "text": "---",
      "char_len": 3,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        8,
        108,
        530,
        123
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 6,
      "serial_label": "L6",
